---
import OptimizedImage from "../components/OptimizedImage.astro";
import SiteLayout from "../components/SiteLayout.astro";
---

<SiteLayout
  title="端云协同的AI检测"
  description="展示车端小模型与云端大模型协同的 AI 检测能力，覆盖事件触发、云端复核、归档和数据闭环。"
  currentPath="/edge-cloud-ai-inspection"
>
  <header class="page-hero inspection-hero">
    <OptimizedImage
      src="/assets/hero-ai-inspection.png"
      webp="/assets/optimized/hero-ai-inspection-1600.webp"
      alt="端云协同 AI 检测场景"
      class="hero-media"
      data-parallax
    />
    <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
    <div class="hero-grid"></div>
    <div class="page-hero-shell">
      <div class="page-hero-copy reveal" data-reveal>
        <p class="page-kicker">PAGE 04 · AI INSPECTION</p>
        <h1 class="page-title">端云协同的AI检测</h1>
        <p class="page-subtitle">
          车端小模型负责快速触发，云端大模型负责复核、归档和持续优化。公开页面展示能力链路；检测体验、历史记录和原图回看进入私有入口后按权限开放。
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="page-main grid-bg">
    <section class="page-section">
      <div class="glass-card section-card reveal" data-reveal>
        <p class="section-kicker">能力说明</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">从车端前置感知到云端数据闭环</h2>
        <div class="page-grid-three">
          <article class="page-card">
            <h3>车端小模型</h3>
            <p>在现场做轻量识别和事件触发，减少无效图片、无效流量和无效告警。</p>
          </article>
          <article class="page-card">
            <h3>云端大模型</h3>
            <p>对复杂事件做语义复核，适合长尾场景、跨场景校验和效果评估。</p>
          </article>
          <article class="page-card">
            <h3>归档复盘</h3>
            <p>保留原图、ROI、时间、地点和判断结果，用于误报分析和模型迭代。</p>
          </article>
        </div>
        <div class="chip-list">
          <a class="chip-item" href="/app/edge-cloud-ai-inspection">进入 AI 检测工作台</a>
          <span class="chip-item">需要检测或历史权限</span>
          <span class="chip-item">服务端先鉴权</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</SiteLayout>

<style>
  .inspection-hero .hero-overlay {
    background:
      linear-gradient(100deg, rgba(2, 6, 23, 0.92), rgba(2, 6, 23, 0.55)),
      radial-gradient(circle at 85% 35%, rgba(251, 146, 60, 0.28), transparent 45%);
  }
  .inspection-hero .page-kicker {
    border-color: rgba(251, 146, 60, 0.38);
    background: rgba(251, 146, 60, 0.08);
    color: #fed7aa;
  }
  .inspection-hero .page-subtitle {
    border-left-color: #fb923c;
  }
</style>
